text: Kopsia larutensis is a species of plant in the family Apocynaceae. It is found in Peninsular Malaysia, Borneo and Thailand. ==References== larutensis Category:Data deficient plants Category:Flora of Peninsular Malaysia Category:Flora of Sarawak Category:Flora of Thailand Category:Plants described in 1908 Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
